  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a Gvfs</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Gvfs</application> package is a userspace virtual
filesystem designed to work with the I/O abstractions of GLib's GIO library.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

